  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study objective is to verify if a non-invasive remote ischemic preconditioning procedure
      (blood pressure cuff on the arm) is cardioprotective when applied before an aortic valve
      replacement surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
